  "purpose": "(Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts of inpatient hospital encounters.),(Data Element Scope: This value set includes class codes used to indicate an inpatient encounter.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent an encounter for inpatient hospitalizations, including short stay visits associated with the inpatient hospitalization.),(Exclusion Criteria: Any class that does not represent inpatient hospitalizations such as ambulatory and virtual visits.)",
